                            Installation instruction
                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Linux
~~~~~
a. From binary (bin) package

   Install:
   # ./mmclient-0.1-i586.bin

   Remove:
   # /opt/mmclient/uninstall

b. From binary (tar.gz) package

   Install:
   # cp mmclient-0.1-i586.tar.gz /opt
   # cd /opt
   # tar -xzf mmclient-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd mmclient
   # ./create_links
            or
   # tar -xzf mmclient-0.1-i586.tar.gz
   # cd mmclient
   # ./install

   Remove:
   # /opt/mmclient/remove_links
   # rm -r /opt/mmclient/
            or
   # /opt/mmclient/uninstall

c. From source package

   Build and install:
   $ tar -xzf mmclient-0.1.tar.gz
   $ ./configure
   $ make
   # make install

   Remove:
   # make uninstall
